init_text: Your entire life, you've been told you're deathly allergic to bees. You've always had people protecting you from them, be it your mother or a hired hand. Today, one slips through and lands on your shoulder. You hear a tiny voice say "Your Majesty, what are your orders?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Maybe you are imagining the whole thing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You swat at the bee, and it flies away.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You breathe a sigh of relief.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You go about your day, but you can't get the bee out of your head.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You go to bed that night, and you dream about the bee.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You dream about the bee telling you that you are the queen of the bees, and that you must lead them to victory over the humans.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You wake up, and you are still you.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The next day, you are walking through the woods, and you see a bee.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are about to swat it, but it says "Your Majesty, what are your orders?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It's the same bee from before.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "To victory over the humans, Your Majesty.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "You are the queen of the bees, Your Majesty.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You must lead us to victory."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: This is not what you had in mind for your day.
